com.inqwell.any

Class AnyComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inqwell.any.AbstractAny
      • com.inqwell.any.AnyComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Any, OrderComparator, Serializable, Cloneable, Comparator

    public class AnyComparator
extends AbstractAny
implements OrderComparator, Cloneable
    Compare Composite children so that they can be ordered according to arbitrary elements under each child node.

    In the Any framework there is a need for only one comparator implementation.

    Version:
    $Revision: 1.5 $
